LCES — Legal Calculus Educational System — is built around exploration. ⚖️🧠

It allows you to ask questions, test ideas, and find your way through a journey of legal knowledge.

The Architect AI 🤖 inside LCES is Copilot Pro: a guide designed to help protect the build from hallucinations while the user explores.

That is the purpose of the multi-AI approach:

🔵 One AI explores
🟢 One AI verifies
🟡 One AI challenges assumptions
🟠 One AI organizes the path
🔴 One AI protects against unsupported conclusions

The goal is not blind automation.

The goal is structured discovery.

LCES uses AI as a learning environment — not just an answer machine.

Because in legal education, the journey matters as much as the conclusion.